claim.claim-text:
1. A removable bezel for personal computer comprising 
a bezel mounted in the front side of a chassis of personal computer, 
a plurality of slot, a plurality of bolt, a plurality of rectangular hole, a plurality of lock socket, 
wherein a plurality of said slots is arranged on the inner surface of said bezel with a bolt inserted into each slot; 
a plurality of said rectangular holes is disposed on the front side of said chassis, corresponding to the location of said bolt; 
said lock socket is installed on each said rectangular hole; 
thereby said bezel is fastened on said chassis by said bolt on the inner surface of said bezel hooked with said lock socket on the front side of said chassis.
